`\n353: 10. ✅ Base URL computed: `{router_url}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/`\n354: 11. ✅ HTTP session with connection pooling (10/10)\n355: 12. ✅ `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id()` raises `ValueError` on missing header\n356: 13. ✅ Package installs via `pip install .`\n357: 14. ✅ Imports work: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient`\n358: 15. ✅ Unit tests cover all clients and error cases (>= 80% coverage)\n359: 16. ✅ Integration tests pass in live environment\n360: 17. ✅ Type hints pass mypy validation\n361: 18. ✅ Code passes ruff/flake8 linting\n362: 19. ✅ Examples provided and runnable\n363: 20. ✅ README documents installation and usage\n364: \n365: ---\n366: \n367: **Notes:**\n368: - Stage ST-3: Design completed, implementation pending\n369: - Session header naming: uses lowercase `x-agentcube-session-id` throughout\n370: - Timeout handling: no buffer needed (unlike CodeInterpreterClient execute_command)\n371: - Session bootstrap: happens in `__init__` if session_id not provided\n372: - No control plane involvement (unlike CodeInterpreterClient)\n373: - Router URL required: no fallback to default, must be provided or in env\n\n(End of file - total 373 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Package Structure & Exports\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Update `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeClient` from `agent_runtime`\n  - Update `__all__` to include `\"AgentRuntimeClient\"`\n  - File: `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verify: `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient` works\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Update `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - Import `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` from `agent_runtime_data_plane`\n  - Add to `__all__` list","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20