{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877345091,"sessionID":"ses_28577793bffeWlqSBWZrdZ4b1w","part":{"id":"prt_d7a89b177001GjbWg8BF1uv1EF","messageID":"msg_d7a89a17b001Ga1YcFTuSkir67","sessionID":"ses_28577793bffeWlqSBWZrdZ4b1w","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-028 change archives:\n\n## AR-028: SDK AgentRuntimeClient — Archive Summary\n\n### What Was Completed ✅\n\n**Core Implementation (100%):**\n- `AgentRuntimeClient` class (`sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`)\n- `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` class (`sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`)\n- Module exports in `agentcube/__init__.py` and `agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Session bootstrapping via GET request to Router invocation endpoint\n- Explicit session ID support (skip bootstrap when provided)\n- Router URL resolution: argument → `ROUTER_URL` env var → `ValueError`\n- Context manager protocol (`with` statement) for automatic cleanup\n- HTTP session with connection pooling (10/10)\n- Timeout defaults: read=120s, connect=5.0s\n- Per-call timeout override in `invoke(timeout=...)`\n- Lowercase header `x-agentcube-session-id` throughout\n\n**Testing (100% coverage):**\n- 32 unit tests passing (100% code coverage)\n- 3 integration tests (skipped without `ROUTER_URL` env var)\n- mypy type checking passed\n\n**Documentation:**\n- README.md with installation, quick start, API reference\n- 2 example files: `agent_runtime_basic.py`, `agent_runtime_explicit_session.py`\n- Comprehensive docstrings in all classes/methods\n- `design.md` and `delta-spec.md` specification documents\n\n### What Was Deferred ⏸️\n\n**None identified** — All 20 acceptance criteria in `tasks.md` are complete. The implementation is production-ready with full test coverage, type hints, documentation, and examples.\n\n**Open Questions** (from delta-spec.md, not implemented but not required):\n1. Exposing additional response metadata beyond parsed JSON\n2. Retry logic for transient HTTP failures\n3. Streaming response support for long-running operations\n4. Agent runtime discovery (list available agents)","time":{"start":1775877345090,"end":1775877345090}}}
